---
// Testimonials Component
---

<section class="py-25 px-6 bg-bg-secondary relative" id="testimoni">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative">
    <div class="text-center max-w-[650px] mx-auto mb-15">
      <span class="inline-block text-[0.875rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-primary mb-3 bg-primary-light px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full">
        Ulasan Wisatawan
      </span>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-[2.5rem] text-text-main mb-4 leading-tight font-extrabold">
        Kisah dari Para Petualang
      </h2>
      <p class="text-text-muted text-[1.125rem]">
        Dengarkan langsung cerita bahagia dari mereka yang telah merasakan keajaiban Banyuwangi bersama layanan kami.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
      <div class="bg-bg-main p-7.5 md:p-12 rounded-3xl shadow-md border border-slate-100/50 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col justify-between relative hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-primary-light group">
        <span class="absolute top-9 right-12 text-primary/8 text-7xl font-serif leading-none pointer-events-none select-none">“</span>
        <p class="text-[1.05rem] leading-relaxed text-text-muted mb-[30px] italic relative z-10">
          "Perjalanan kami ke Kawah Ijen sangat berkesan berkat Travel Osing! Pemandu lokal kami, Mas Haris, tahu persis rute terbaik agar kami terhindar dari keramaian dan mendapat posisi berfoto Blue Fire tercantik. Benar-benar profesional!"
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full overflow-hidden border-3 border-white shadow-md">
            <img class="w-full h-full object-cover" src="/images/avatar1.png" alt="Foto Client Ardelia Maharani" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="text-left">
            <h4 class="text-base font-bold text-text-main">Ardelia Maharani</h4>
            <p class="text-[0.8rem] text-text-light font-semibold">Trip Kawah Ijen Premium</p>
            <div class="flex gap-0.5 text-accent text-[0.95rem] mt-1">
              <span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
      <div class="bg-bg-main p-7.5 md:p-12 rounded-3xl shadow-md border border-slate-100/50 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col justify-between relative hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-primary-light group">
        <span class="absolute top-9 right-12 text-primary/8 text-7xl font-serif leading-none pointer-events-none select-none">“</span>
        <p class="text-[1.05rem] leading-relaxed text-text-muted mb-[30px] italic relative z-10">
          "Pengalaman budaya di Kemiren sungguh otentik. Kami diajak mencicipi kopi khas di rumah warga dan diajari memainkan Angklung. Rasanya seperti berkunjung ke rumah keluarga sendiri. Anak-anak sangat menikmati sabana Baluran!"
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full overflow-hidden border-3 border-white shadow-md">
            <img class="w-full h-full object-cover" src="/images/avatar2.png" alt="Foto Client Gede Wirawan" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="text-left">
            <h4 class="text-base font-bold text-text-main">Gede Wirawan</h4>
            <p class="text-[0.8rem] text-text-light font-semibold">Trip Family Baluran & Budaya</p>
            <div class="flex gap-0.5 text-accent text-[0.95rem] mt-1">
              <span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
